          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Choose this header mode when youâ€™re using hierarchical data sources if you want to be able to expand and collapse the header."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When you use this header mode, a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicollectionviewlistcell"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object that appears as the first item in the section automatically uses a header appearance. When you configure your data source, make sure to account for the fact that the first item in the section (at index "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ") represents the header, and the actual items in the section start at index "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "1"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "By default, lists that use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicollectionlayoutlistappearance/uicollectionlayoutlistappearanceplain"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicollectionlayoutlistappearance/uicollectionlayoutlistappearancesidebarplain"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " list appearances use pinned headers. If you want to opt into this default pinning behavior, use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uicollectionlayoutlistheadermode/uicollectionlayoutlistheadermodesupplementary"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " header mode instead. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        }
      ]
    }
